Revision history for Test-Spelling-Comment

{{$NEXT}}

  - Use redefine() instead of mock() from Test::MockModule
  - Switch license to the ISC license
  - Moved test files depending on additional modules to xt and skip them
    during installation testing
  - Removed test dependency on Test::Fatal

0.005  2019-08-03 23:39:53 UTC

  - API change: all_files_ok() no longer takes files or directories as
    arguments. The files to be tested is now obtained from XT::Files.

0.004  2018-06-25 18:13:37 UTC

  - Removed minimal dependency on Test::TempDir::Tiny 0.017
  - Use g flag for the substitution with the skip patterns

0.003  2018-06-24 19:35:33 UTC

  - added argument skip to new

0.002  2018-06-22 22:39:27 UTC

  - add_stopwords returns $self instead of undef to allow chaining
  - fixed abstract

0.001  2018-06-21 20:05:26 UTC

  - Initial release
